than I thought.

04:57.760 --> 05:00.991
My nose was just an insane amount
of money.

05:01.080 --> 05:02.877
I mean, I was shocked.

05:02.960 --> 05:07.317
I thought that a nose job
was only, like, three or four grand,

05:07.400 --> 05:09.311
but I was wrong.

05:09.400 --> 05:13.313
Mine was, like,
three times that amount.

05:13.400 --> 05:16.756
I mean, my girlfriend's
breast enlargement

05:16.840 --> 05:20.116
was, like, four or five grand.

05:20.480 --> 05:26.316
I mean, it's not like
I ever felt them, but...

05:27.440 --> 05:32.036
They actually look kinda real,
you know?

05:34.960 --> 05:38.589
<i>So your own wife, who's hot,</i>
<i>by the way, with big jugs,</i>

05:38.680 --> 05:40.033
<i>won't even go down on you?</i>

05:40.160 --> 05:42.628
<i>You can call my girlfriend</i>
<i>and she'll tell you,</i>

05:42.720 --> 05:44.915
<i>and I've been with her</i>
<i>for quite a while,</i>

05:45.000 --> 05:48.754
<i>and she will tell you she goes down</i>
<i>on me every time we're together.</i>

06:52.240 --> 06:54.754
You're a disgrace to white folks.

07:53.280 --> 07:54.713
Christ!

08:01.920 --> 08:03.990
Where's my wallet?

08:10.920 --> 08:12.433
Where's my wallet?

08:12.520 --> 08:15.114
- On the dresser.
- Hi, Sister Jean, it's Joe.

08:16.560 --> 08:17.959
Sure.

08:19.280 --> 08:22.875
How can you spend a thousand bucks
on a 976 line?

08:22.960 --> 08:26.111
I don't get it. You're Joseph Scott,
who every woman wants,

08:26.200 --> 08:28.156
and you waste your money
on a 976 line.

08:28.240 --> 08:31.755
Cos I can pretend to be someone else.

08:31.840 --> 08:36.072
Not you, Sister Jean, someone else.
I need some tickets.

08:36.159 --> 08:39.277
I'm at home. Now?

08:41.679 --> 08:44.911
Great, thank you.
I'll see you in a bit. Bye. Bye.

08:45.000 --> 08:49.152
Don't you have any philosophies
in life apart from self-indulgence?

08:49.240 --> 08:51.959
You're the most self-indulgent fool
I've ever met.

08:52.040 --> 08:54.918
- I thought you'd given up.
- I did give up.

08:55.360 --> 08:57.874
And then I started again. Feel this.

08:59.240 --> 09:01.470
- What?
- Feel this. It's a lump.

09:02.320 --> 09:04.959
Feel that lump? You feel it?
There? There!

09:07.040 --> 09:08.951
It's cancer.

09:10.000 --> 09:12.639
Breast cancer.
Can men get breast cancer?

09:14.680 --> 09:19.390
Do they give men mastectomies?
I've got something down there as well.

09:19.480 --> 09:22.870
- Have you seen a doctor?
- Yes, and he's a fucking idiot!

09:22.960 --> 09:24.712
It's cancer.

09:26.840 --> 09:29.593
- So where is it?
- What?

09:29.680 --> 09:31.875
- My wallet!
- On the dresser.

09:31.960 --> 09:33.632
- No, it isn't.
- It is.

09:34.120 --> 09:36.350
What the fuck is that?

09:36.440 --> 09:39.989
- That would be a dog.
- Why the fuck is it in my house?

09:41.040 --> 09:42.359
Apple!

09:49.320 --> 09:51.470
- <i>Hello?</i>
- Apple.

09:51.560 --> 09:53.790
- <i>Hi, Joe.</i>
- Why did you leave your dog here?

09:53.880 --> 09:55.677
- <i>You said I could.</i>
- No, I didn't.

09:55.760 --> 10:00.436
<i>Yes, you did. I'll pick him up at the</i>
<i>restaurant after your lunch meeting.</i>

10:00.520 --> 10:02.715
I'm not taking that dog to lunch
with me.

10:02.800 --> 10:05.917
<i>Don't bring him into the restaurant.</i>
<i>Leave him in the car.</i>

10:06.000 --> 10:07.797
<i>I'll be there at two.</i>

10:09.200 --> 10:10.872
You better.

10:31.960 --> 10:34.394
Is it cocktail hour yet?

10:40.120 --> 10:42.554
Well, it is somewhere!

10:49.960 --> 10:51.518
I'm handing in my notice.

10:52.840 --> 10:54.159
Why?

10:55.280 --> 10:57.510
It's so much fun here.

10:59.320 --> 11:00.912
How much?

11:01.000 --> 11:03.719
- It's not about the money.
- How much?

11:03.800 --> 11:06.837
When I show up here,
I never know what to expect.

11:06.920 --> 11:10.959
Whether you've eaten mushrooms
or acid or coke or all of the above.

11:11.040 --> 11:14.350
You know what they call you?
Captain Wacky.

11:14.440 --> 11:16.351
Captain Wacky.

11:16.440 --> 11:20.228
You know, I really don't like
looking at myself through your eyes.

11:22.440 --> 11:24.032
Another 500.

11:25.320 --> 11:26.594
I'm not happy.

11:27.520 --> 11:30.637
Your happiness doesn't interest me.
Mine does.

11:31.840 --> 11:33.353
600.

11:38.080 --> 11:39.752
700.

11:42.240 --> 11:46.153
- OK.
- That's a month, not a week.

12:34.440 --> 12:35.668
Yes?

12:37.080 --> 12:39.150
- Yes?
- <i>Hi!</i>

12:53.680 --> 12:56.353
Hi! You look terrific.

12:56.440 --> 12:59.512
So do you. Welcome. Come in.
Nice to see you.

13:00.760 --> 13:03.877
My apartment block was shaking
last night. Did you feel it?

13:03.960 --> 13:05.757
No.

13:05.840 --> 13:09.071
I thought it was gonna fall in
and I was gonna die.

13:11.440 --> 13:12.998
Five, right?

13:13.760 --> 13:17.958
You have the fires and you have
the floods and you have the riots...

13:19.720 --> 13:22.439
And then you have
the drive-by shootings.

13:23.280 --> 13:26.955
Fires, floods, earthquakes, riots.

13:27.880 --> 13:30.917
I drove by a body on my way here
just lying on the sidewalk.

13:31.000 --> 13:33.798
We don't need to go to the movies.
We live in a movie.

13:33.920 --> 13:34.989
We do!

13:35.080 --> 13:38.356
I live here, but I can't find
a good thing to say about it.

13:38.440 --> 13:43.468
If I close my eyes and picture it,
all I see is one big varicose vein.

13:47.640 --> 13:50.518
You got yourself a dog!

13:50.600 --> 13:53.239
It's good to have animals.

13:54.720 --> 13:57.518
I have two dogs, two cats
and a green lizard.

13:57.600 --> 14:00.990
I had two boa constrictors
that I got when they were babies.

14:01.080 --> 14:03.435
They were always
getting out of their tank.

14:03.520 --> 14:07.559
When they got to about six foot,
one wrapped itself around the treadmill.

14:07.640 --> 14:10.313
- I turned it on and it got flattened!
- No!

14:10.400 --> 14:13.437
I've had so many animals,
you wouldn't believe it.

14:13.520 --> 14:14.873
Snakes, eh?

14:17.360 --> 14:19.430
Well, I'd better be going.

14:22.000 --> 14:24.958
You're not into smack?
I got some straight off the boat.

14:25.040 --> 14:26.314
No.

14:26.400 --> 14:28.595
Smack junkies
never seem to get bored.

14:28.680 --> 14:32.912
They can look at their shoes for eight
hours and still have a good time.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.956
I envy that.

14:35.040 --> 14:37.235
Well, it's nice to see you, Joe.

14:37.320 --> 14:40.039
Nice to see you, Sister Jean.

14:45.560 --> 14:48.791
- Thanks for coming.
- No problem. I'll see you soon. Bye.

14:48.880 --> 14:50.677
Bye-bye now.

14:54.080 --> 14:56.514
Will you help me with this dog?

14:57.360 --> 14:59.555
What do you mean "help"?

14:59.640 --> 15:02.029
If people see me with it,
they'll think I'm gay.

15:02.120 --> 15:04.759
- See? That was easy.
- Why didn't you do it yourself?

15:04.840 --> 15:07.912
I'm meeting an important director.
I don't want hairs on me.

15:08.720 --> 15:10.995
- Oh, Christ!
- Oh, my God!

15:11.080 --> 15:12.593
- Christ!
- Can we help?

15:12.680 --> 15:15.877
I'm sorry! Fucking dog! I'm so sorry.
We're fine, thank you.

15:15.960 --> 15:17.678
I was talking to the lady!

15:17.760 --> 15:20.593
If you need a witness
to that assault, I'd be...

15:20.680 --> 15:24.753
What are you talking about? It wasn't
an assault, it was an accident.

15:24.840 --> 15:28.230
That was no accident. It was
an unprovoked, vicious attack!

15:28.320 --> 15:30.356
I'm calling the police right now!

15:30.440 --> 15:32.795
It was an accident!
I wouldn't hit her.

15:32.880 --> 15:36.668
I saw you and I know you.
I know all about you, Joe Scott.

15:36.760 --> 15:40.275
Put your cellphone away.
It was an accident, not an assault.

15:40.360 --> 15:42.920
You ladies are old enough
to know the difference.

15:43.000 --> 15:45.719
If you don't get outta here,
there will be an assault!

15:45.800 --> 15:50.112
We were trying to help! He shouldn't get
away with it! You should report him!

15:50.200 --> 15:53.670
You saw what you wanted to see!
Get outta here! You understand me?

15:56.320 --> 15:58.197
God!

16:04.120 --> 16:05.872
Put that on your nose.

16:07.560 --> 16:09.198
Come and sit down.

16:12.720 --> 16:14.756
Step in.

16:16.560 --> 16:20.872
There you go. Steady.
Put your head back. There you go.

16:28.080 --> 16:30.514
I... I'll make you some tea, shall I?

16:30.600 --> 16:32.875
You don't know how to make tea.

16:34.640 --> 16:37.108
- You're gonna leave me, aren't you?
- What?

16:39.360 --> 16:40.554
You're gonna leave me.

16:40.640 --> 16:43.234
Are you gonna stand there
with your thumb up your ass

16:43.320 --> 16:44.878
or are you gonna get the phone?

16:44.960 --> 16:48.748
Is that a roundabout way of saying
you don't wanna discuss it right now?

16:49.440 --> 16:50.668
- Hello?
- <i>Joe?</i>

16:50.760 --> 16:52.751
- Hi, Mum.
- <i>You picked up the phone!</i>

16:52.840 --> 16:55.308
- <i>Where's Ophelia?</i>
- Busy. Can I call you back?

16:55.400 --> 16:59.075
- I'm in the middle of something.
- <i>Joe, I've got some bad news.</i>

16:59.160 --> 17:01.071
- What, are you OK?
- <i>Yes, I'm fine.</i>

17:01.160 --> 17:04.152
- Is Peggy OK?
- <i>No, Peggy's fine.</i>

17:04.240 --> 17:06.435
<i>I hate to tell you this</i>
<i>over the phone.</i>

17:06.520 --> 17:08.157
Just tell me!

17:10.800 --> 17:11.993
Mum?

17:13.359 --> 17:16.511
- Mum, are you there?
- <i>Oh, dear...</i>

17:16.599 --> 17:19.512
- For God's sake, tell me!
- <i>Joe, I'm so sorry.</i>

17:19.599 --> 17:21.750
Just tell me, Mum, please.

17:21.839 --> 17:23.910
<i>Boots has died.</i>

17:25.160 --> 17:26.752
What?

17:28.800 --> 17:30.518
<i>Boots has died.</i>

17:31.520 --> 17:34.637
When... Boots has died?

17:34.720 --> 17:38.030
- When?
- <i>Yesterday. It happened yesterday.</i>

17:38.120 --> 17:40.156
<i>I'm so sorry, Joe.</i>

17:42.600 --> 17:43.828
How?

17:44.880 --> 17:47.758
<i>They're not sure yet.</i>
<i>There has to be an autopsy.</i>

17:51.760 --> 17:53.671
<i>Joe?</i>

17:53.760 --> 17:56.035
Yeah. Yeah, Mum, I'm here.

17:58.680 --> 18:01.717
<i>They're holding the funeral</i>
<i>at Saint Joseph's.</i>

18:01.800 --> 18:06.237
<i>Ruth would love you to come,</i>
<i>but she understands if you're too busy.</i>

18:08.640 --> 18:11.313
<i>Joe, it's been such a shock to her.</i>

18:11.400 --> 18:14.790
<i>He wasn't even ill. There was no</i>
<i>warning that this was coming.</i>

18:17.760 --> 18:20.513
<i>I feel terrible telling you this</i>
<i>over the phone.</i>

18:24.320 --> 18:26.880
<i>I know you haven't seen him for years,</i>

18:26.960 --> 18:30.157
<i>but I know how much you meant</i>
<i>to each other.</i>

18:30.240 --> 18:34.711
<i>He was so proud of you</i>
<i>and all that you've achieved.</i>

18:51.600 --> 18:54.114
- Can you get me a Bloody Mary?
- Certainly, sir.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.668
I'm so sorry I'm late.
The traffic was dreadful.

18:56.760 --> 19:00.036
Joe Scott, Hollywood's hottest
young director, Ritchie Smith.

19:00.120 --> 19:03.351
How are you doing? The script
is fantastic. Congratulations.

19:03.440 --> 19:06.113
Mannie says you've directed
some music videos.

19:06.200 --> 19:08.998
Did you look at 'em?
Fuckin' awesome, ain't they?

19:09.080 --> 19:11.355
- You didn't send them to me.
- We didn't?

19:11.440 --> 19:12.873
No.

19:15.160 --> 19:17.310
Excuse me. Hello?

19:17.400 --> 19:21.837
Yeah. What do you mean? I've been
trying to get hold of you for days.

19:21.920 --> 19:24.718
Yes, I have! Now is not a good time.

19:26.080 --> 19:29.197
Don't call me when
I'm in a fucking lunch meeting!

19:30.120 --> 19:32.190
I am serious! I'll talk to you later.

19:32.280 --> 19:36.068
- Can I get another one?
- Why didn't you call the office?

19:36.160 --> 19:40.517
That's the place to call, not when
I'm having lunch, OK? Call me later.

19:40.600 --> 19:42.238
Sure. Bye.

19:43.920 --> 19:48.152
Sorry about that. There'll be a tape
at your house when you get home, OK?

19:49.240 --> 19:51.356
OK, let's order some food!

19:55.800 --> 19:57.916
OK. This stuff looks good, huh?

19:59.120 --> 20:01.998
I had a big breakfast.
I'm just gonna have a salad.

20:02.080 --> 20:03.559
Yeah, so am I.

20:04.320 --> 20:05.992
Hello?

20:07.240 --> 20:09.276
Dave! How are you, my man?

20:12.400 --> 20:14.914
No, that's great.

20:25.160 --> 20:28.277
Sure, we'll talk later. OK, bye.

20:29.600 --> 20:32.876
Let's order! Excuse me?

20:34.160 --> 20:36.993
- I'm gonna have a green salad.
- Yeah, for me as well.

20:39.240 --> 20:42.118
- Ritchie, want anything?
- Burger.

20:42.200 --> 20:44.634
- Burger.
- How would you like that?

20:44.720 --> 20:47.598
- Rare?
- He'd like it rare.

20:47.680 --> 20:51.195
- Anything else I can get you?
- Ritchie, anything else?

20:51.280 --> 20:53.316
No. No, thank you.

20:55.320 --> 20:57.356
Thank you.

20:58.120 --> 20:59.269
Sorry.

21:01.560 --> 21:04.154
I have to go to the bathroom.

21:04.240 --> 21:05.719
Sure.

21:11.400 --> 21:12.515
OK.

21:13.560 --> 21:17.519
Business. Things have developed a lot
since we last spoke, OK?

21:17.600 --> 21:21.036
And since Ritchie started casting
seriously, he...

21:23.240 --> 21:25.435
