21:25.520 --> 21:28.432
he realises your character
isn't going the way he wants.

21:28.520 --> 21:31.671
You know how things are.
You start casting, things change,

21:31.760 --> 21:34.399
- dynamics change...
- Dynamics?

21:34.480 --> 21:38.439
Yeah. You know, dynamics.
Dynamics between characters.

21:39.720 --> 21:41.233
He wants to go younger.

21:43.880 --> 21:45.154
Hello?

21:45.960 --> 21:47.678
George!

21:49.800 --> 21:51.791
How are ya?

21:53.320 --> 21:55.754
That's great!
I tell you what you do, though.

21:55.840 --> 21:58.957
You take the $35 million,
you go to Brazil.

21:59.040 --> 22:02.919
You keep $34 million for yourself
and spend $1 million on a picture.

22:03.000 --> 22:07.039
Only don't spend it on this one. This...
What the fuck are you doing?

22:07.120 --> 22:10.510
- Are you trying to humiliate me?
- That's my fuckin' phone!

22:10.600 --> 22:12.909
Why didn't you say on the phone?
Why am I here?

22:13.000 --> 22:17.551
I... Goddamn it, when did you become
such an asshole? What date exactly?

22:17.640 --> 22:20.473
I thought Ritchie might give you
another part.

22:20.560 --> 22:23.393
- Have you read the script?
- Course I read the script.

22:23.480 --> 22:25.357
- Have you read the script?
- Yes.

22:25.440 --> 22:27.396
If you'd read the fuckin' script,

22:27.480 --> 22:31.155
you'd know there are only
four characters and three are women!

22:31.240 --> 22:35.233
So which other fucking part
do you think I might be right for?

22:35.320 --> 22:37.390
No other fuckin' part!

22:38.320 --> 22:42.359
I don't think there's any part
in any script for you, anywhere!

22:42.440 --> 22:44.476
No one's interested any more, Joe!

22:44.560 --> 22:48.838
And you know why not?
Because you're not interested any more!

22:48.920 --> 22:52.913
You have squandered every fuckin'
opportunity you've ever been given!

22:53.000 --> 22:56.356
Take a look in the mirror next time
you're snorting off it,

22:56.440 --> 22:58.396
because you are a mess!

22:58.480 --> 23:01.950
I am tired of pretending otherwise,
so I'm giving it to you straight.

23:02.040 --> 23:05.191
It is over. You are over.

23:05.280 --> 23:07.748
People are tired
of your pathetic behaviour.

23:07.840 --> 23:10.513
They don't wanna be around it
any more. Neither do I!

23:10.600 --> 23:14.434
So you know what I suggest? I suggest
you get yourself a new agent!

23:43.360 --> 23:44.998
Cool dog!

23:45.080 --> 23:46.718
- What?
- Brussels Griffon.

23:46.800 --> 23:48.791
- Brussels what?
- Brussels Griffon.

23:48.880 --> 23:52.111
- The Jack Nicholson dog.
- Yeah, the fucking dog. Thanks.

23:59.720 --> 24:02.280
- <i>Hello?</i>
- Where are you, Apple?

24:02.360 --> 24:04.316
<i>Hi, Joe!</i>

24:04.400 --> 24:07.472
Can you explain to me
why your dog is still in my car?

24:07.560 --> 24:09.676
- <i>I need a big favour.</i>
- No.

24:09.760 --> 24:13.719
- <i>Would look after him for a few days?</i>
- A few days? Are you insane?

24:13.800 --> 24:15.279
<i>I have to go away.</i>

24:15.360 --> 24:18.909
- You are not dumping your dog on me.
- <i>I'm not dumping him on you!</i>

24:19.000 --> 24:21.036
- <i>Just a few days.</i>
- What's that smell?

24:22.600 --> 24:26.229
Jesus!
Your dog has done a shit in my car!

24:26.320 --> 24:28.038
<i>Joe?</i>

24:28.120 --> 24:30.395
- No...
- <i>Joe?</i>

24:30.480 --> 24:32.391
- Don't hang up!
- <i>I'm losing you.</i>

24:32.480 --> 24:33.993
Don't hang up on me. Please!

24:34.080 --> 24:36.753
- <i>Can't hear you.</i>
- Don't hang up!

24:36.840 --> 24:38.876
Fuck! Fuck!

24:43.400 --> 24:46.119
You like the dog?
Keep the fucking dog.

29:10.240 --> 29:11.832
Hey, Joe?

29:13.160 --> 29:15.674
You know David Bowie
believes in aliens?

29:15.760 --> 29:17.318
