29:32.280 --> 29:35.033
Well, how often do you have a bath then?

29:35.400 --> 29:37.311
- Every day.
- Every day?

29:37.400 --> 29:40.915
- Yes, every day.
- What, does your mum make you?

29:41.000 --> 29:43.560
No, I just like to be clean.

29:44.720 --> 29:47.996
Every day's not clean.
Every day's weird.

29:51.400 --> 29:54.039
- D'you remember that ginger girl?
- Shut up!

30:11.120 --> 30:12.439
Come on.

30:19.400 --> 30:21.868
Hang on, I can't even see!

30:21.960 --> 30:23.359
Joe!

30:24.440 --> 30:25.668
Joe!

30:25.760 --> 30:27.352
Wait here.

30:27.440 --> 30:28.475
Alright?

30:28.560 --> 30:30.551
Go round the side.

31:30.400 --> 31:31.913
- Wotcher.
- Wotcher.

31:32.000 --> 31:36.152
Hello. You're late.
You missed lunch.

31:37.000 --> 31:39.833
- Who are you?
- I'm Boots.

31:39.920 --> 31:41.638
What kind of name is that?

31:44.640 --> 31:48.315
